hare%20all%20relevant%20information%20in%20time%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-disclose-details-on-electoral-bonds-data-in-time-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-5231416%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20Amendment%20Rules%20a%20'Deceptive%20Instrument'%3A%20Citizens'%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26164434%2FCitizenship_Amendment_Act_protests_in_Guwahati.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20group%20of%20citizens%20have%20issued%20a%20statement%20and%20call%20for%20protest%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202024%2C%20notified%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20the%20statement%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cviolates%20several%20key%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20undermines%20the%20secular%20basis%20of%20Indian%20citizenship%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20highlights%20how%20several%20petitions%20against%20the%20CAA%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%20citizens%20of%20India%20unanimously%20condemn%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202024%20(CAR%2C%202024)%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20on%20March%2011%2C%202024%2C%20as%20a%20sinister%20ploy%20to%20sow%20discord%20and%20division%20across%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20of%20the%20collective%20view%2C%20shared%20by%20millions%20of%20citizens%2C%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019%20(CAA%2C%202019)%20violates%20several%20key%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20undermines%20the%20secular%20basis%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Over%20two%20hundred%20petitions%20are%20pending%20in%20the%20highest%20judiciary%20since%20December%202019%2C%20challenging%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20of%20the%20CAR%2C%202024%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20amounts%20to%20an%20unwarranted%20interference%20in%20a%20sub%20judice%20matter.%20We%20appeal%20to%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20his%20companion%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20stay%20the%20operationalisation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202024%20till%20the%20final%20verdict%20is%20delivered%20on%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20consider%20the%20CAR%2C%202024%20as%20a%20deceptive%20instrument%20to%20identify%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20in%20Indian%20states%20like%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Assam%2C%20Tripura%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20which%20are%20home%20to%20millions%20of%20post-Partition%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh%20(erstwhile%20East%20Pakistan).%20For%20decades%2C%20such%20refugees%20who%20have%20permanently%20settled%20in%20India%20have%20been%20enrolled%20as%20voters%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20and%20thereby%20entitled%20to%20all%20the%20rights%20associated%20with%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%20through%20naturalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20CAA%2C%202003%20which%20introduced%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20citizenship%20law%2C%20prevented%20the%20post-Partition%20refugees%20from%20becoming%20Indian%20citizens%20through%20naturalisation%20and%20laid%20down%20the%20draconian%20and%20exclusionary%20processes%20of%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Indian%20Citizens%2C%20by%20eliminating%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20citizens%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20National%20Population%20Register.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Home%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Narrative%E2%80%99%20on%20CAA%20is%20Full%20of%20Lies%2C%20Half-Truths%20and%20Really%20Bad%20Drafting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministrys-positive-narrative-on-caa-is-full-of-lies-half-truths-and-really-bad-drafting%5C%22%3EHome%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Narrative%E2%80%99%20on%20CAA%20is%20Full%20of%20Lies%2C%20Half-Truths%20and%20Really%20Bad%20Drafting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NRC%20process%20in%20Assam%2C%20conducted%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20led%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20over%2019%20lakh%20persons%20in%20the%20final%20NRC%20published%20in%20July%202019.%20The%20fate%20of%20these%20persons%20still%20remains%20uncertain%2C%20pushing%20them%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20statelessness%20and%20robbing%20them%20of%20their%20social%20and%20economic%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20The%20pathetic%20experience%20of%20Assam%20NRC%2C%20which%20shifted%20the%20burden%20of%20proof%20of%20citizenship%20to%20the%20citizens%2C%20itself%20should%20have%20ended%20further%20effort%20to%20conduct%20any%20NRC-type%20processes%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20CAR%2C%202024%20does%20precisely%20that%20by%20requiring%20applicants%20for%20naturalisation%20or%20registration%20as%20Indian%20citizens%20to%20submit%20the%20particulars%20of%20their%20birthplace%2C%20parents%20birthplace%2C%20religion%20and%20date%20of%20entry%20into%20India%2C%20alongside%20Passport%20and%20expired%20Visa.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20such%20applications%20would%20be%20rejected%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CEmpowered%20Committee%E2%80%9D%20under%20CAR%2C%202024%20because%20the%20required%20documents%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20applicants.%20The%20rejected%20applicants%20would%20evidently%20become%20non-citizens%20or%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20the%20CAR%2C%202024%20becoming%20a%20witch%20hunt%20for%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20migrants%E2%80%9D%20is%20further%20confirmed%20by%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20sudden%20deactivation%20of%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20persons%2C%20particularly%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20under%20Regulation%2028A%20of%20Aadhaar%20(Enrolment%20and%20Update)%20Regulations%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Regulation%2028A%2C%20newly%20inserted%20in%20September%202023%2C%20empowers%20the%20Aadhaar%20authority%20to%20determine%20and%20regulate%20Indian%20citizenship%20and%20decide%20whether%20a%20person%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20national%E2%80%9D%2C%20going%20beyond%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20parent%20Aadhaar%20Act%2C%202016%20which%20categorically%20excludes%20grant%20or%20determination%20of%20citizenship.%20We%20condemn%20such%20arbitrary%20and%20illegal%20deactivation%20of%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20under%20Regulation%2028A%20and%20demand%20its%20immediate%20nullification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20call%20upon%20the%20People%20of%20India%20to%20reject%20any%20attempt%20to%20rob%20the%20citizenship%20and%20other%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20Indian%20residents%20on%20a%20mass-scale%2C%20through%20exclusionary%20processes%20envisaged%20in%20the%20NRC%2C%20NPR%2C%20CAA%202003%2C%20CAA%202019%2C%20Regulation%2028A%20of%20Aadhaar%20Rules%20and%20the%20latest%2C%20CAR%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20invite%20all%20secular%20and%20democratic%20minded%20citizens%2C%20representatives%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20mass%20organisations%2C%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20platforms%20who%20are%20committed%20to%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20basic%20values%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20for%20a%20Roundtable%20Dialogue%20on%20Citizen