26quot%3BThat's%20great%20for%20the%20hobbyist%2C%20but%20it's%20terrifying%20for%20the%20military%20defender.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-shoot-balloons-learn-to-defeat-dangerous-drone-threat-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0ae8b90413ab8e1dbe87b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-shoot-balloons-learn-to-defeat-dangerous-drone-threat-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20military%20is%20training%20service%20members%20to%20counter%20the%20rising%20threat%20of%20small%20drones%2C%20which%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-shoot-balloons-learn-to-defeat-dangerous-drone-threat-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20looks%20like%20Costco's%20%241.50%20hot%20dog%20deal%20might%20not%20be%20around%20forever%20after%20all%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Costco%20food%20court.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F645fb9ba11971c00188f3d43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222680%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECostco's%20%241.50%20hot%20dog%20and%20soda%20combo%20deal%20has%20been%20on%20the%20menu%20since%201985.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Rose%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECostco's%20longtime%20CFO%20once%20said%20the%20chain%20would%20offer%20its%20%241.50%20hot%20dog%20deal%20forever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20in%20a%20new%20interview%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20question%20its%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%