C%20saying%20that%20the%20veteran%20played%20the%20best%20knock%20for%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20liked%20his%20(Musheer)%20approach%20and%20his%20partnership%20with%20Iyer%20may%20have%20made%20things%20difficult%20for%20Vidrabha.%20But%20the%20best%20knock%20I%20think%20came%20from%20Ajinkya%20(73).%20He%20scored%20those%20runs%20when%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umesh%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1258-umesh-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20good%20spell.%20Now%20with%20so%20many%20runs%20on%20the%20board%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20Vidarbha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjeuu17k8_shreyas-iyer-pti_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdelivered-when-it-mattered-kkr-coach-on-fearless-shreyas-iyer-after-ranji-heroics-5229284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%20scored%2095%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20against%20Vidarbha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Short%20On%20Names%20For%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20BJP%20And%20KCR%20Party%20Fight%20Over%20Candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20Telangana%20today%20fought%20over%20a%20former%20MLA%20who%20had%20announced%20he%20would%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20BRS%20MLA%20Aroori%20Ramesh%20was%20at%20home%20when%20BRS%20leaders%20barged%20in%20and%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20take%20him%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Ramesh%20yesterday%20met%20Telangana%20BJP%20chief%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%2C%20the%20former%20BRS%20leader%20announced%20he%20would%20join%20the%20BJP%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BRS%2C%20former%20state%20minister%20Errabelli%20Dayakar%20and%20others%20barged%20in%20and%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20convince%20Mr%20Ramesh%20not%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%20They%20reportedly%20made%20him%20speak%20to%20BRS%20leader%20Harish%20Rao%20on%20phone%2C%20after%20which%20they%20allegedly%20forced%20Mr%20Ramesh%20into%20a%20car%20to%20take%20him%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20where%20senior%20BRS%20leaders%20including%20Mr%20Rao%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20would%20be%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20supporters%20clashed%20outside%20Mr%20Ramesh's%20house%20when%20word%20spread%20he%20had%20been%20allegedly%20'kidnapped'%20by%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20visuals%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20is%20seen%20being%20pulled%20out%20of%20a%20car%20in%20which%20Errabelli%20Dayakar%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20front%20seat.%20The%20car%20was%20reportedly%20intercepted%20by%20BJP%20supporters%20and%20stopped%20from%20going%20towards%20to%20Hyderabad.%20The%20BJP%20supporters%20dialled%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20and%20made%20Mr%20Ramesh%20speak%20to%20him%20in%20front%20of%20cameras%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20he%20would%20tell%20the%20BRS%20leadership%20he%20has%20quit.%20Visuals%20showed%20the%20former%20MLAs%20shirt%20had%20been%20torn%20in%20the%20scuffle.%20He%20looked%20hassled%20and%20confused%20about%20what%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20find%20candidates%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20lost%20three%20MPs%20in%20recent%20times%20-%20one%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20two%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Ranjith%20Reddy%20from%20Chevella%20has%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20reportedly%20wanted%20to%20field%20Mr%20Ramesh%20from%20Warangal%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20the%20same%20offer%2C%20and%20he%20preferred%20the%20party%20that%20is%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20told%20reporters%20he%20was%20humiliated%20in%20the%20BRS%20despite%20winning%20with%20a%20good%20majority%20in%20the%20past%20and%20wanted%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20does%20not%20have%20enough%20candidates%20with%20potential%20to%20win%20and%20so%20is%20looking%20to%20induct%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20is%20now%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20after%20its%20defeat%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20BRS%20MP%20BB%20Patil%20from%20Zaheerabad%20a%20day%20after%20he%20joined%20the%20party%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BRS%20had%20wanted%20to%20make%20him%20contest%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20made%20Bharat%20Prasad%20its%20candidate%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20(Scheduled%20Castes%20reserved)%20constituency%20just%20two%20days%20after%20his%20father%20and%20MP%20P%20Ramulu%20resigned%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20leader%20B%20Vinod%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20party%20from%20Karimnagar%2C%20said%20five%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20candidates%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20are%20from%20the%20BRS%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20BRS%20MPs%20Ajmeera%20Sitaram%20Naik%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20(Adilabad)%2C%20and%20two%20former%20MLAs%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20(Kothagudem)%20and%20S%20Saidi%20Reddy%20(Huzurnagar)%2C%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20BRS%20leader%2C%20G%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20from%20Peddapalli%2C%20has%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc25v2qag_aroori-ramesh_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID