ggerheart%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20answer%20to%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20game%20master%20Matthew%20Mercer%2C%20the%20team%20went%20on%20Twitch%20to%20give%20a%20four-hour%20live%20demonstration%20of%20its%20new%20gaming%20system.%20Thousands%20of%20viewers%20tuned%20in.%20It's%20not%20often%20that%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20board%20game%20gets%20the%20airtime%20this%20one%20is%20getting%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitch-channel-critical-role-was-top-earning-channel-in-leak-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECritical%20Role%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20more%20than%201.3%20million%20followers%20on%20Twitch%2C%20and%20the%20cast%20members%20have%20dedicated%20fanbases%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDaggerheart%26quot%3B%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20lore%2C%20magic%2C%20and%20monsters%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20built%20around%20classic%20role-playing%20game%20elements%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erolling%20dice%2C%20character%20sheets%2C%20and%20combat%20mechanics.%20The%20game%20also%20involves%20a%20card%20system%20that%20outlines%20a%20character's%20history%20and%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cast%20also%20introduced%20their%20audience%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tumblr.com%2Fquinn-of-aebradore%2F744800834168160256%3Fsource%3Dshare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20slate%20of%20character%20types.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ever%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20monkey%20with%20healing%20powers%20or%20a%20wizard%20who%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20beetle%3F%20Yep%2C%20that's%20possible%2C%20since%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20elves%2C%20dwarves%2C%20and%20goblins%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritical%20Role%20CEO%20and%20core%20cast%20member%20Travis%20Willingham%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20September%20that%20the%20company's%20investment%20in%20Darrington%20Press%20%E2%80%94%20the%20publishing%20arm%20through%20which%20these%20gaming%20systems%20are%20being%20released%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20exciting%20and%20rewarding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20frankly%20just%20overjoyed%20with%20the%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20Willingham%20said%20of%20the%20game%20systems'%20early%20playtest%20at%202023's%20GenCon.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20this%20is%20us%20just%20kind%20of%20figuring%20it%20out%20as%20we%20go%20and%20giving%20it%20our%20best%20shot.%20And%20we%20know%20that%20won't%20always%20be%20enough%2C%20but%20when%20there's%20a%20positive%20reception%20to%20it%2C%20it's%20extremely%20rewarding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20too%20soon%20to%20say%20how%20successful%20Critical%20Role's%20new%20launch%20will%20be%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BDaggerheart%26quot%3B%20open%20beta%20is%20a%20potential%20game%20changer%20for%20RPG%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20marks%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20first%20edition%20of%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-dungeons-and-dragons-dnd-module-free-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20game%20that%20counts%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20including%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20its%20fans.%20To%20celebrate%20the%20anniversary%2C%20Wizards%20of%20the%20Coast%2C%20the%20game's%20current%20owner%2C%20is%20launching%20One%20D%26amp%3BD%2C%20a%20codename%20for%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20the%20game%2C%20with%20updated%20rulesets%20and%20digital%20play%20options.%20This%20launch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdndbeyond-support.wizards.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F8609273323156-One-D-D-FAQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomes%20with%20a%20series%20of%20books%2C%20slated%20for%20release%20in%20late%202024%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20used%20with%20the%20immensely%20popular%20fifth%20edition%20of%20the%20game%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Critical%20Role%20helped%20to%20popularize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20One%20D%26amp%3BD%20was%20not%20without%20controversy.%20The%20previous%20edition's%20Open%20Game%20License%2C%20or%20OGL%2C%20allowed%20creators%20to%20publish%20and%20profit%20from%20work%20compatible%20with%20the%20game.%20Not%20so%20with%20One%20D%26amp%3BD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Wizards%20of%20the%20Coast%20tried%20to%20introduce%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Fdungeons-dragons-ogl-license-wizards-of-the-coast-wotc-1849985196%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20version%20of%20the%20OGL%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20require%20that%20independent%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20work%20helped%20the%20game's%20pop%20culture%20resurgence%20%E2%80%94%20report%20sales%20and%20give%20Hasbro%20a%20cut%20of%2020-25%25%20of%20sales%20above%20%24750%2C000%2C%20Gizmodo%20reported%2C%20citing%20a%20leaked%20copy%20of%20the%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Finvesting%2F2023%2F01%2F17%2Fbig-change-coming-for-hasbro-should-investor-worry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Motley%20Fool%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20while%20D%26amp%3BD%20provided%2022%25%20of%20Hasbro's%20annual%20revenue%2C%20it%20created%2078%25%20of%20its%20profit.%20The%20attempted%20cash%20grab%20associated%20with%20the%20new%20OGL%20caused%20prominent%20third-party%20publishers%20to%20balk%2C%20and%20they%20began%20working%20on%20their%20own%20systems.%20Fans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdungeons-dragons-dnd-wizards-of-the-coast-licensing-ogl-controversy-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolted%20and%20vowed%20to%20burn%20the%20game%20to%20the%20ground%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hasbro%20went%20into%20damage-control%20mode%2C%20eventually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dndbeyond.com%2Fposts%2F1423-an-update-on-the-open-game-license-ogl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C