rn%20Blk%20Girl's%20mission%20is%20to%20close%20the%20gender%20investing%20and%20racial%20wealth%20gaps%20and%20get%20500%2C000%20women%20of%20color%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-the-stock-market%5C%22%3Estock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20is%20to%20encourage%20youth%20to%20invest%2C%20to%20get%20them%20in%20that%20mindset%2C%20so%20they're%20saving%20for%20that%20first%20car%2C%20for%20college.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20be%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20in%20those%20formative%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Brookes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20they're%20working%20to%20change%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arielinvestments.com%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FPDF%2Fariel-schwab-black-investor-survey-gender-race-age-october2021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderrepresentation%20of%20Black%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20Modern%20Blk%20Girl%20is%20an%20educational%20community%20that%20offers%20classes%20on%20investing.%20Its%20free%20Teen%20University%2C%20a%20four-week%2C%20accelerated%20financial%20literacy%20program%20for%20young%20women%20ages%2014%20to%2019%2C%20teaches%20how%20to%20invest%20in%20and%20navigate%20the%20stock%20market.%20Each%20student%20receives%20a%20%24500%20cash%20wallet%20to%20get%20started.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20two%20people%20are%20selected%20to%20receive%20a%20%2410%2C000%20grant%20for%20college.%2010%20young%20people%20are%20chosen%20every%20other%20month%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModern%20Blk%20Girl%20has%20grown%20its%20community%20to%20more%20than%20150%2C000%20members%20and%20helped%20women%20of%20color%20earn%20more%20than%20%243.5%20million%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-stock-trading-apps%5C%22%3Estock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20some%20of%20the%20questions%20that%20keep%20coming%20up%20from%20community%20members%20and%20what%20she%20tells%20them%2C%20and%20what%20she%20tells%20women%20who%20are%20afraid%20to%20start%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%202%20most%20common%20questions%20she%20gets%20about%20investing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20asked%20questions%20from%20the%20MBG%20community%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20do%20I%20begin%3F%26quot%3B%20says%20Brookes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20answer%3F%20%26quot%3BLook%20around%20you.%20What%20cellphone%20do%20you%20use%2C%20what%20car%20do%20you%20drive%2C%20what%20video%20games%20do%20your%20kids%20play%3F%20Invest%20in%20companies%20you%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20quick%20to%20buy%20expensive%20purses%20or%20spend%20money%20on%20a%20vacation%2C%26quot%3B%20Brookes%20continues.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20have%20to%20have%20an%20ownership%20mentality%20versus%20a%20spending%20mentality.%20OK%2C%20if%20you%20buy%20the%20bag%2C%20be%20rewarded%20with%20that%20purchase%20if%20you%20also%20own%20stock%20in%20the%20company%20that%20made%20the%20bag.%20There%20is%20a%20stock%20related%20to%20everything%20in%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20common%20question%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20money%20should%20I%20start%20with%3F%26quot%3B%20Brookes%20says%20there%20is%20no%20standard%20answer%20to%20that%20one.%20It%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20person's%20financial%20circumstances.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20start%20with%20a%20small%20amount%2C%20a%20few%20hundred%20to%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars.%20We%20encourage%20people%20to%20use%20simulated%20trading%20before%20they%20put%20up%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20investing%20successfully%20is%20learning%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20MBG%20members%20are%20first-time%20investors%2C%20and%20investing%20wasn't%20dinner%20table%20talk%20when%20they%20were%20growing%20up.%20Brookes%20gets%20it.%20She%20had%20some%20initial%20fears%20herself.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20thing%20when%20I%20was%20investing%20my%20summer%20camp%20money%20I%20made%20in%20high%20school%2C%20but%20when%20I%20started%20working%2C%20that%20was%20another%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20tells%20those%20who%20are%20fearful%20that%20education%20is%20the%20best%20antidote%20to%20fear.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20do%20your%20research%2C%20when%20you%20put%20the%20work%20in%2C%20you'll%20feel%20more%20confident.%26quot%3B%20That's%20how%20she%20got%20over%20her%20own%20fear%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20internet%20was%20my%20best%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20as%20she%20turned%20to%20sources%20like%20Yahoo%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20and%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20too%2C%20she%20brings%20home%20the%20point%20that%20investing%20is%20not%20a%20short-term%20play.%20%26quot%3BPatience%20pays%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20incorrectly%20think%20if%20they%20invest%20and%20trade%2C%20they'll%20be%20an%20overnight%20success.%20But%20that's%20like%20thinking%20you%20go%20to%20school%20and%20after%20one%20class%20you've%20mastered%20the%20subject.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20learning%20can%20help%20make%20sense%20of%20a%20complicated%20world.%20%26quot%3BBig%20words%20can%20be%20confusing.%20Industry%20insiders%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20translate%20concepts%20when%20they're%20teaching%20the%20stock%20market%20so%20that%20people%20understand%20them.%20That's%20why%20we%20took%20off%3A%20We%20break%20stuff%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brookes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20discipline%20is%20key%20to%20investing%20success.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20be%20emotional.%20You%20need%20emotional%20discipline%20to%20be%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20If%20you%20had%20a%20down%20day%2C%20while%20over%20the%20short-term%20it's%20discouraging%2C%20in%20the%20long%20term%20it's%20just%20one%20down%20day.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20started%20out%2C%20she%20didn't%20have%20the%20community%20MBG%20provides.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20family.%20We%20joke.%20We%20aren't%20only%20about%20finances%2C%20but%20this%20community%20touches%20on%20spirituality%20and%20wellness.%20It's%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20learn%2C%20to%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brookes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20easy%20to%20change%20people's%20mindsets%20about%20money%20and%20investing%2C%20but%20Brookes%20doesn't%20get%20weary%20in%20well%20doing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20remember%20the%20bigger%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20and%20calls%20MBG's%20work%20a%20blessing.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20purpose%20in%20what%20we%20are%20doing.%20There%20is%20a%20movement%20to%20close%20the%20racial%20and%20generational%20wealth%20gap.%20Our%20legacy%20will%20be%20that%20we%20educated%20our%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EWealthfront%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-robo-advisors%5C%22%3Ebest%20robo-advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20investing%20options%20for%20low-cost%20automated%20or%20self-managed%20portfolios.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwealthfront-review%5C%22%3EWealthfront%20investing%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-women-of-color-modern-blk-girl-2024-03%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710326461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62879e28577b8a001827b7a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-women-of-color-modern-blk-girl-2024-03%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharlea%20Brookes%20cofounded%20Modern%20Blk%20Girl%20to%20encourag