0in%20the%20state%20of%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20in%20the%20state%20saw%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20March%207%20directive%20as%20a%20move%20to%20mollify%20the%20STs%20of%20Goa%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20the%20community%20in%20the%20assembly.%20The%20hurry%20in%20which%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20passed%20the%20directive%2C%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20its%20tenure%2C%20can%20be%20appreciated%20better%20if%20one%20recalls%20Goa%20chief%20minister%20Pramod%20Sawant%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20last%20month.%20Sawant%20had%20told%20the%20House%20then%20that%20the%20reservation%20of%20assembly%20constituencies%20for%20STs%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20before%20the%20delimitation%20process%20expected%20countrywide%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20just%20days%20to%20go%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20the%20Centre%20made%20a%20sudden%20move%20on%20Goa.%20This%20matches%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%E2%80%99s%20other%20recent%20express%20moves%20where%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20immediate%20political%20motive%20discernible%2C%20keeping%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20poll%20prospects%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20is%20focused%20on%20micro-managing%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20This%20approach%20of%20the%20party%20to%20utilise%20the%20Central%20government%E2%80%99s%20powers%20to%20add%20leverage%20to%20its%202024%20prospects%2C%20in%20turn%20puts%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20so-called%20invincibility%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Modi%20factor%E2%80%99%20on%20voters.%20Also%2C%20it%20calls%20to%20question%20how%20confident%20the%20party%20is%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20issue%2C%20beyond%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20At%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%2C%20Modi%20pushed%20his%20way%20to%20play%20priest-king%2C%20casting%20all%20religious%20and%20secular%20convention%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Goa%20directive%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Sawant%E2%80%99s%20February%2011%20statement%20in%20the%20Goa%20assembly%2C%20mentioned%20above%2C%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20calling-attention%20motion%20moved%20by%20the%20entire%20seven-member%20Opposition%20belonging%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Revolutionary%20Goan%20Party%20and%20Goa%20Forward%20Party.%20For%20over%20a%20year%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20strident%20protest%20in%20Goa%20around%20this%20demand.%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20bandwagon%2C%20leaving%20Sawant%20a%20bit%20wary%20about%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20meeting%20the%20target%20of%20winning%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20also%20announced%20that%20day%20that%20he%20would%20visit%20New%20Delhi%20on%20February%2016%20to%20press%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20to%20grant%20the%20demand.%20As%20planned%2C%20he%20met%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20February%2019%20in%20Delhi.%20Shah%2C%20without%20spelling%20out%20any%20deadline%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Famit-shah-promises-to-resolve-st-quota-issue-for-polls-pramod-sawant%2Farticleshow%2F107816800.cms%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20resolve%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2024%2C%20Sawant%20met%20Shah%20again%2C%20this%20time%20with%20a%20sizeable%20delegation%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20ST%20community.%20Once%20again%2C%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heraldgoa.in%2FGoa%2FCMled-delegation-meets-Amit-Shah-on-ST-reservation%2F218187%5C%22%3Eassured%20them%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20ST%20leaders%20had%20by%20then%20declared%20that%20they%20would%20boycott%20the%202024%20elections%20if%20their%20demand%20was%20not%20met%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%202011%20census%2C%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20ST%20population%20was%20at%2010.23%25%2C%20which%20in%20the%20last%2013%20years%20may%20have%20gone%20up.%20The%20ST%20population%20is%20a%20decisive%20factor%20in%20the%20South%20Goa%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20succeeded%20in%20increasing%20its%20country-wide%20tally%20from%20the%20one%20in%202014%2C%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20win%20in%20South%20Goa.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Francisco%20Sardinha%20had%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20a%20slim%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Goa%20constituency%2C%20which%20the%20party%20won%20in%202019%2C%20also%20has%20significant%20numbers%20of%20ST%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20placate%20the%20agitation%20leaders.%20According%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20they%20have%20rejected%20the%20decision%20since%20it%20is%20still%20a%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscontent%20aside%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20poll%20strategies%20aimed%20particularly%20at%20smaller%20communities%20which%20can%20be%20the%20deciding%20factor%20in%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20assembly%20or%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20often%20the%20pattern%20is%20only%20to%20heap%20layer%20upon%20layer%20of%20promises%20to%20keep%20their%20hope%20tied%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20promise%20since%20the%202014%20general%20elections%20to%20the%20Matua%20voters%20of%20Bengal%20(by%20promising%20them%20first%20to%20pass%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20and%20then%20to%20implement%20the%20Act)%2C%20or%20to%20the%20Gorkha%2FNepali%20community%20particularly%20influential%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20(to%20grant%20them%20the%20Gorkhaland%20state)%2C%20the%20pattern%20is%20all%20too%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20agreement%20for%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20new%20front%2C%20based%20on%20this%20strategy%20of%20promises%20to%20a%20smaller%20group%20just%20before%20an%20election%2C%20has%20now%20been%20opened%20in%20Tripura%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime.%20The%20Modi-era%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20now%20openly%20majoritarian%20in%20its%20approach%2C%20has%20been%20pussy-footing%20the%20demand%20for%20Greater%20Tipraland%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20minority%20ST%20community%20for%20some%20time%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%202024%20elections%20looming%2C%20the%20tribal%20party%2C%20Tipra%20Motha%2C%20which%20is%20now%20the%20largest%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20and%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20demand%2C%20announced%20that%20its%20leader%2C%20the%20well-recognised%20ex-royal%2C%20Pradyut%20Debbarma%2C%20would%20embark%20on%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20protest%20to%20seek%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20demand.%20The%20party%20also%20began%20hobnobbing%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Opposition%20for%20a%20united%20fight%20in%20the%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Goa%2C%20Tripura%20also%20has%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20While%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20Bengali%20population%20is%20the%20deciding%20factor%20in%20the%20West%20Tripura%20constituency%2C%20the%20East%20Tripura%20seat%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20ST%20community.%20In%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20BJP%20had%20cornered%20the%20seat%20(along%20with%20the%20West%20Tripura%20seat)%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20verbal%20promise%20to%20the%20tribal%20leaders%20to%20look%20into%20the%20Tipraland%20demand.%20Lately%20though%2C%20the%20birth%20and%20meteoric%20rise%20of%20Tipra%20Motha%20which%20demanded%20no%20less%20than%20a%20written%20promise%20from%20the%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20on%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%2C%20made%20it%20an%20imperative%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20bring%20it%20to%20its%20side%2C%20lest%20the%20seat%20be%20won%20by%20the%20opposition%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%20another%20express%20decision%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20It%20entered%20into%20a%20written%20agreement%20with%20Tipra%20Motha%20to%20settle%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20constitutional%20protection.%20Though%20a%20written%20promise%20has%20allowed%20the%20Tipra%20Motha%20to%20go%20to%20the%20community%20as%20a%20winner%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20it%20is%20not%20too%20different%20from%20the%20Goa%20promise.%20Both%20the%20promises%20are%20just%20that%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mere%20promise%20to%20look%20into%20the%20demands%20sometime%20in%20the%20future.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20moves%20urgently%20made%20by%20the%20government%20keeping%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20forthcoming%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%208%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20declared%20former%20Tripura%20chief%20minister%20Biplab%20Kumar%20Deb%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20the%20West%20Tripura%20seat%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20East%20Tripura%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20political%20observers%20in%20the%20state%20to%20deduce%20that%20it%20would%20most%20likely%20be%20set%20aside%20for%20a%20consensus%20tribal%20candidate%20belonging%20to%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20aligned%20to%20the%20NDA%20including%20Tipra%20Motha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromises%20in%20Ladakh%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20is%20likely%20to%20try%20the%20Goa-Tripura%20strategy%20in%20Ladakh%20too%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20(UT)%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnrest%20in%20the%20UT%20has%20been%20simmering%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20Led%20by%20local%20hero%20and%20climate%20activist%2C%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20the%20inspiration%20for%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20character%20in%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20people%20have%20been%20seeking%20inclusion%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20protect%20their%20land%2C%20culture%20and%20environment.%20Wangchuk%20is%20currently%20on%20a%2021-day%20%E2%80%98climate%E2%80%99%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20Ladakhi%20leaders%20seeking%20constitutional%20protection%20and%20statehood%20to%20Ladakh%20met%20Amit%20Shah%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-positive-outcome-in-meeting-with-amit-shah-say-ladakh-bodies%2Farticle67913708.ece%5C%22%3Emeeting%20was%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20rounds%20of%20shutdowns%20have%20paralysed%20life%20in%20Leh-Ladakh%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20Shah%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20March%2C%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Cpromises%E2%80%9D%20to%20match%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20Ladakhis.%20Quoting%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20March%202%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fjammu-and-kashmir%2Fannouncement-on-parts-of-sixth-schedule-status-to-ladakh-during-home-minister-amit-shahs-visit-2919132%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Shah%20is%20likely%20to%20announce%20%E2%80%9Csome%20parts%20of%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%20to%20the%20region%20during%20his%20visit%20later%20this%20month%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reference%20was%20to%20a%20report%20being%20readied%20by%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visit%20(of%20Shah)%20could%20happen%20either%20before%20the%20imposition%20of%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20or%20during%20the%20poll%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20like%20in%20the%20STs%20of%20Tripura%20and%20Goa%2C%20a%20promise%20is%20in%20the%20offing%20for%20the%20STs%20of%20Ladakh%20too%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20clearly%20aiming%20at%20pocketing%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromise%20in%20Gorkhaland%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20poll-bound%20promises%2C%20the%20Gorkhas%2FNepalis%20of%20Darjeeling%20have%20to%20be%20appreciated%20the%20most%2C%20for%20their%20patience%20with%20the%20BJP.%20They%20have%20been%20continuously%20electing%20a%20BJP%20MP%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20Darjeeling%20seat%20since%202009.%20In%202014%2C%20hopes%20rose%20particularly%20high%20because%20the%20party%2C%20with%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20promised%20Gorkhaland%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20no%20promises%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20party%20even%20after%20ten%20years%20of%20Modi%20rule%2C%20the%20Darjeeling%20areas%20have%20been%20witnessing%20angry%20protests%20of%20late.%20Sensing%20the%20public%20mood%2C%20the%20BJP%20Darjeeling%20MLA%20Neeraj%20Zimba%2C%20on%20March%203%2C%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20with%20his%20blood%20to%20Modi%2C%20reminding%20him%20that%20he%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cdreams%20of%20the%20Gorkhas%20are%20my%20dreams%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20neighbouring%20Siliguri%20this%20March%207%2C%20once%20again%20promised%20to%20keep%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20promise%20of%20Gorkhaland.%20Clearly%2C%20he%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20patience%20of%20the%20Gorkhas%20can%20be%20tested%20in%202024%20too%20for%20the%20party%20to%20retain%20the%20Darjeeling%20seat%20this%20time.%20Like%20in%20Goa%20and%20Tripura%2C%20this%20promise%20is%20also%20an%20open-ended%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmplified%20protest%20in%20Eastern%20Nagaland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20hesitated%20to%20repeat%20its%20promises%20to%20sets%20of%20voters%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20their%20hope%20going%2C%20the%20party%20is%20not%20in%20any%20hurry%20to%20fulfil%20at%20least%20one%20promise%20its%20Union%20government%20had%20made%20to%20a%20group%20of%20people%20in%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20since%20early%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20People%E2%80%99s%20Organization%20(ENPO)%2C%20the%20outfit%20that%20has%20been%20spearheading%20the%20demand%20in%20six%20frontier%20districts%20of%20Nagaland%20for%20the%20Frontier%20Nagaland%20Territory%20(FNT)%2C%20has%20declared%20a%20%E2%80%98public%20emergency%E2%80%99%20and%20boycott%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%20No%20political%20party%20is%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20even%20campaign%20in%20these%20districts%2C%20till%20the%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20fulfil%20its%20promise%20made%20to%20ENPO%20to%20carve%20out%20FNT%20from%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20promise%20had%20helped%20the%20BJP%20pocket%20several%20seats%20in%20the%20eastern%20Nagaland%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20polls%2C%20making%20it%20the%20second%20largest%20in%20the%2060-member%20Nagaland%20assembly%20first%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20Nagaland%20having%20only%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20ENPO%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20necessary%20weight%20to%20drive%20the%20Modi%20government%20towards%20making%20any%20move%20in%20its%20favour%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20decided%20to%20put%20up%20a%20consensus%20NDA%20candidate%20for%20the%20Nagaland%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131044%2FGINxSf5WcAAw8wr.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-t