versation%20with%20Faith%20Larkum%2C%20a%20student%20who%20participated%20in%20a%20FluCamp%20trial.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20freshman%20in%20my%20first%20term%20of%20university%20when%20I%20saw%20a%20FluCamp%20ad%20on%20my%20Instagram%20feed.%20It%20explained%20you%20could%20get%20paid%20for%20participating%20in%20a%20clinical%20trial.%20As%20a%20broke%20university%20student%2C%20I%20was%20intrigued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20slightly%20suspicious%20about%20the%20company's%20legitimacy%2C%20but%20after%20a%20background%20check%2C%20it%20all%20seemed%20real%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20applied%20to%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20a%20clinical%20trial%20testing%20flu%20medicine%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFluCamp%20called%20the%20next%20day%2C%20inviting%20me%20for%20a%20blood%20test%20and%20explaining%20how%20the%20trial%20worked.%20The%20premise%20of%20the%20trial%20is%20you're%20injected%20with%20a%20diluted%20flu%20virus%20and%20then%20given%20either%20medicine%20or%20a%20placebo.%20You%20spend%20two%20weeks%20in%20a%20private%20room%20getting%20routinely%20tested%2C%20with%20your%20symptoms%20monitored%20by%20nurses%20and%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20paid%20%C2%A34%2C500%2C%20about%20%245%2C756%2C%20for%20two%20weeks%20of%20doing%20almost%20nothing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20contributing%20to%20medical%20science%20while%20doing%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20good%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20telling%20me%20I'd%20passed%20the%20screening%20and%20was%20eligible.%20The%20blood%20tests%20are%20used%20to%20check%20that%20you're%20fit%20and%20healthy%20enough%20to%20take%20part%2C%20so%20there%20are%20minimal%20health%20risks%20for%20participants.%20They%20told%20me%20I%20could%20do%20the%20trial%20during%20the%20Christmas%20vacation%20before%20returning%20to%20my%20studies%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20intense%20isolation%20and%20needles%20concerned%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20some%20reservations.%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20how%20isolated%20I'd%20be%20during%20the%20trial%20because%20I'm%20very%20much%20an%20extrovert.%20The%20other%20worry%20I%20had%20was%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20blood%20tests%20you%20have%20to%20do%20because%20I%20sometimes%20pass%20out%20giving%20blood.%20I%20did%20pass%20out%20a%20few%20times%2C%20but%20by%20the%20end%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20pro%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20get%20over%20my%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20to%20a%20few%20of%20the%20doctors%20before.%20I%20asked%20them%20how%20sick%20I%20would%20get%20and%20whether%20I'd%20be%20bedbound%20the%20whole%20time.%20The%20doctor%20assured%20me%20there's%20a%20very%20low%20risk%20that%20you'd%20get%20very%2C%20very%20ill.%20People%20will%20likely%20experience%20some%20mild%20cold%20or%20flu-like%20symptoms%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20I%20felt%20fine%20the%20entire%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20you%20get%20briefed%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20with%20the%20other%2015%20or%20so%20people%20taking%20part%20in%20FluCamp's%20trial.%20It%20was%20a%20complete%20mix%20of%20ages%20and%20genders.%20Once%20that's%20over%2C%20you%20go%20to%20your%20private%20room%20with%20an%20en-suite%20bathroom.%20You're%20on%20your%20own%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20time%20there%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20the%20visits%20from%20doctors%20and%20nurses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENothing%20happens%20for%20the%20first%20few%20days%3B%20then%2C%20you're%20injected%20with%20the%20virus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20aren't%20injected%20with%20the%20flu%20for%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20the%20trial.%20I%20was%20just%20chilling%2C%20doing%20my%20university%20work.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou're%20injected%20with%20a%20diluted%20flu%20virus%20and%20given%20the%20medicine%20or%20a%20placebo%20a%20few%20days%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20a%20FluCamp%20staff%20member%20gave%20us%20a%20tick%20sheet%20to%20fill%20out%20every%20morning%20about%20how%20we%20felt%20and%20whether%20we%20had%20any%20symptoms.%20Doctors%20would%20come%20in%20about%20four%20times%20daily%20to%20test%20your%20vitals%2C%20like%20a%20blood%20test%2C%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20EKG.%20Other%20than%20that%2C%20you're%20just%20left%20to%20your%20own%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20have%20to%20make%20your%20own%20fun%20during%20a%20medical%20trial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20binge-watched%20movies.%20I%20read%20a%20book%20in%20like%20three%20hours.%20I%20was%20journaling%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20introspection.%20I%20had%20three%20or%20four%20essays%20for%20university%2C%20and%20I%20just%20banged%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20entertainment%20you're%20given%20is%20a%20PS4%20and%20a%20few%20different%20games.%20FluCamp%20said%20anything%20else%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20in.%20I%20did%20have%20to%20keep%20finding%20different%20things%20to%20entertain%20myself%20because%20it%20quickly%20became%20monotonous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20is%20unlimited%2C%20so%20you%20can%20order%20as%20much%20as%20you%20want%20from%20this%20app%20you%20download.%20I%20tried%20to%20order%20a%20different%20thing%20each%20day%20until%20I'd%20exhausted%20all%20the%20options.%20I%20liked%20a%20lasagne%20and%20rice%20dish%2C%20and%20the%20sandwiches%20were%20delicious.%20You%20can%20always%20ask%20for%20extra%20snacks%20like%20popcorn%2C%20crisps%2C%20and%20cereal%20bars.%20The%20food%20was%20all%20right%2C%20but%20there%20could%20have%20been%20more%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENot%20being%20allowed%20outside%20or%20to%20exercise%20was%20tough%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20I%20found%20the%20hardest%20was%20probably%20the%20lack%20of%20fresh%20air.%20You're%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20facility%2C%20and%20my%20window%20opened%20an%20inch.%20You%20can't%20socialize%20with%20anyone%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20allowed%20to%20exercise%20either%20because%20they%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20if%20you%20recover%20faster%20or%20slower%20than%20others%2C%20it%20isn't%20because%20you've%20exercised.%20So%20I%20just%20felt%20really%20lazy%20and%20gross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardest%20point%20was%20eight%20days%20in.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it%20was%20only%20halfway%20over.%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%3A%20can%20I%20do%20this%3F%20I'd%20done%20all%20my%20work%3B%20I'd%20started%20several%20TV%20series%20and%20given%20up.%20I%20enjoy%20films%20and%20series%20as%20much%20as%20the%20next%20person%2C%20but%20after%20the%20trial%2C%20I'd%20completely%20maxed%20out%20my%20capacity%20for%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20desperate%20to%20get%20out%20by%20the%20end%2C%20but%20I'll%20do%20it%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enjoyed%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40faithlarks%2Fvideo%2F7185235319678110981%3F_r%3D1%26_t%3D8iZ3kvyfG2D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikToks%20every%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20walking%20people%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bday%20in%20the%20life%26quot%3B%20of%20flu%20camp%2C%20and%20reading%20all%20the%20comments%20%E2%80%94%20that%20kept%20me%20going.%20I%20should%20have%20bought%20more%20fiction%2C%20as%20escapism%20would've%20gone%20a%20long%20way.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'll%20bring%20in%20more%20artsy%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20like%20drawings%2C%20paintings%2C%20or%20my%20ukulele%20%E2%80%94%20activities%20that%20will%20reduce%20my%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20paid%20%C2%A34%2C500%2C%20about%20%245%2C756%2C%20for%20the%20two-week%20trial.%20I%20went%20in%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20saving%20that%20money%20as%20a%20buffer%20while%20I%20studied%20on%20top%20of%20my%20student%20loans.%20But%20then%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20it%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20much%20I%20don't%20like%20being%20alone.%20Toward%20the%20end%2C%20I%20was%20desperate%20to%20get%20out.%20I%20assumed%20I%20was%20more%20of%20an%20introvert%20than%20I%20am%20and%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20need%20people%20and%20socializing.%20It's%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20money%2C%20and%20I've%20signed%20up%20again%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-to-do-nothing-clinical-trial-side-hustle-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710324540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f051aa6080194819feeddd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-to-do-nothing-clinical-trial-side-hustle-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Getting%20paid%20to%20do%20nothing%20is%20an%20appealing%20side%20hustle.%20Student%20Faith%20Larkum%20made%20thousands%20for%20participating%20in%20a%20two-week%20clinical%20trial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Daisy%20Schofield)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-to-do-nothing-clinical-trial-side-hustle-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NHAI%20asks%20Paytm%20FASTag%20users%20to%20switch%20to%20another%20issuing%20bank%20by%20March%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710324472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F13%2Ffull%2F1710324215-7833.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fnhai-asks-paytm-fastag-users-to-switch-to-another-issuing-bank-by-march-15-124031300512_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20will%20help%20avoid%20penalties%20or%20double%20fee%20charges%20while%20commuting%20on%20National%20Highways%2C%20as%20per%20the%20statement%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fnhai-asks-paytm-fastag-users-to-switch-to-ano