29.69%25%20in%20the%20previous%20month.%20Even%20potato%20prices%2C%20which%20had%20been%20in%20negative%20territory%20since%20February%202023%2C%20surged%20by%2012.38%25%20last%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffood-inflation-rises-to-8-66-in-feb-as-vegetable-prices-soar-jan-industrial-output-slows%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B22%2C217%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Bought%20From%202019-24%2C%20Of%20Which%2022%2C030%20Redeemed%26quot%3B%3A%20SBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20a%20rap%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20today%2C%20informing%20that%20it%20had%20submitted%20data%20on%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(EC).%C2%A0The%20SBI%20has%20said%20in%20its%20compliance%20affidavit%20that%20it%20has%20submitted%20the%20data%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20in%20a%20pen%20drive.%20The%20data%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20is%20on%20two%20PDF%20files%20that%20are%20password-protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20also%20said%20in%20its%20affidavit%20that%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C217%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20issued%20between%20April%202019%20and%20February%2015%2C%202024%2C%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20junked%20the%20scheme.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20political%20parties%20redeemed%2022%2C030%20bonds.%20The%20remaining%20187%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20were%20redeemed%20and%20the%20money%20deposited%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20national%20relief%20fund%2C%20according%20to%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20donors%20could%20purchase%20bonds%20to%20donate%20to%20parties%20of%20their%20choice.%20But%20the%20parties%20had%20to%20redeem%20the%20bonds%20within%2015%20days%2C%20failing%20which%20the%20amount%20would%20go%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20relief%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20landmark%20February%2015%20verdict%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bviolates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20citizens%2C%20about%20possible%20quid%20pro%20quo%26quot%3B%20between%20donors%20and%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%20had%20been%20ordered%20to%20stop%20issuing%20the%20bonds%20immediately%20and%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20the%20donations%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20which%20would%20make%20them%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%206%20for%20SBI%20to%20submit%20the%20data%2C%20and%20the%20EC%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20make%20it%20public%20by%20March%2013.%20But%20the%20bank%20requested%20the%20court%20for%20an%20extension%20till%20June%2030.%20This%20was%20challenged%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20which%20was%20among%20the%20petitioners%20who%20had%20opposed%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20court%20turned%20down%20the%20SBI's%20request%20and%20said%20it%20must%20share%20the%20details%20by%20Tuesday.%20The%20EC%20has%20now%20been%20asked%20to%20upload%20the%20data%20on%20its%20website%20by%205%20pm%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20SBI%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20had%20said%20the%20bank%20had%20followed%20an%20SOP%20to%20store%20information%20about%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20outside%20the%20core%20banking%20system.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20full%20details%20on%20who%20purchased%20the%20bond%20and%20I%20have%20full%20details%20from%20where%20the%20money%20came%20from%20and%20which%20political%20party%20tendered%20how%20much.%20I%20have%20to%20also%20now%20put%20the%20name%20of%20purchasers.%20The%20names%20have%20to%20be%20collated%2C%20cross-checked%20with%20the%20bond%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20court%20replied%20that%20it%20has%20not%20asked%20the%20bank%20to%20match%20the%20donors%20with%20the%20amount%20received%20by%20political%20parties.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20asked%20you%20to%20do%20the%20matching%20exercise.%20So%20to%20seek%20time%20saying%20that%20a%20matching%20exercise%20is%20to%20be%20done%20is%20not%20warranted%2C%20we%20have%20not%20directed%20you%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710316500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4l1gu19o_sbi-_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20a%20rap%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20today%2C%20informing%20that%20it%20had%20submitted%20data%20on%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(EC).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waheeda%20Rehman%2C%20Indian%20Cinema%20Legend%2C%20Donates%20Personal%20Film%20Memorabilia%20to%20Film%20Heritage%20Foundation%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710316423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0