leshow%2F108458391.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDo%20You%20Get%20Runs%20Outside%20India%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Anderson%20On%20Sledging%20Gill%2C%20Reveals%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELegendary%20England%20pacer%20James%20Anderson%20on%20Tuesday%20revealed%20what%20he%20said%20to%20star%20Indian%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%20in%20their%20exchange%20of%20words%20during%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20between%20both%20sides%20at%20Dharamsala.%20On%20Day%20three%20of%20the%20match%2C%20England's%20ageless%20pace%20wonder%20Anderson%20had%20become%20the%20first%20pacer%20ever%20to%20reach%20700%20Test%20wickets.%20One%20of%20his%20two%20victims%20during%20India's%20first%20innings%20was%20Gill%2C%20who%20had%20scored%20a%20fine%20century%2C%20concluding%20what%20could%20be%20a%20breakthrough%20Test%20series%20after%20a%20string%20of%20low%20scores%20on%20a%20high.%20Just%20before%20Gill%20had%20reached%20his%20century%2C%20he%20exchanged%20some%20words%20with%20the%2041-year-old%20pacer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20in%20the%20post-day%20press%20conference%2C%20Gill%20had%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20Wisden%20on%20his%20exchange%20with%20Anderson%2C%20%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20both%20of%20us%20to%20keep%20that%20chat%20in%20private.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Anderson%20has%20spilled%20the%20beans.%20Talking%20on%20BBC%20Tailenders%20Podcast%20as%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo%2C%20Anderson%20revealed%20that%20he%20taunted%20Gill%20about%20his%20overseas%20Test%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%20something%20to%20him%20like%2C%20'Do%20you%20get%20any%20runs%20outside%20India%3F'%20and%20he%20said%2C%20'It's%20time%20to%20retire.%20Then%20two%20balls%20later%2C%20I%20got%20him%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2010%20Tests%20away%20from%20home%2C%20Gill%20has%20scored%20556%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2032.70%2C%20with%20a%20century%20and%20two%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20110.%20Gill's%20record%20in%20India%20though%20is%20much%20superior%2C%20scoring%20869%20runs%20in%2013%20Tests%20at%20an%20average%20of%2041.38%2C%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%20four%20fifties%20in%2023%20innings.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20128.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20had%20a%20fine%20series%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20ending%20as%20the%20second-highest%20run-getter%20with%20452%20runs%20in%20nine%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2056.5%2C%20with%20two%20centuries%20and%20two%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20was%20110.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnderson%20also%20reflected%20on%20his%20700th%20Test%20wicket%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20do%20at%20the%20picturesque%20venue%20of%20Dharamsala%20with%20his%20father%20around.%20But%20it%20would%20have%20been%20better%20had%20they%20won%20the%20series.%20He%20said%20however%20that%20he%20enjoyed%20the%20tour%20a%20lot.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20play%20cricket%20for%20milestones%20and%20winning%20gives%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20buzz%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20nice%20moment%20and%20nice%20to%20do%20it%20(take%20700th%20wicket)%20at%20a%20picturesque%20ground.%20My%20dad%20was%20here%20so%20we%20had%20a%20drink%2C%20which%20was%20nice.%20He%20was%20more%20excited%20than%20I%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20I%20would%20have%20felt%20more%20excited%20if%20we%20had%20have%20won%20the%20Test%20or%20the%20series.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20long%20series%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20know%20how%20I%20feel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20get%20anything%20out%20of%20that%20(about%20milestones%20and%20whether%20someone%20will%20touch%20his%20record).%20I%20do%20not%20get%20anything%20out%20of%20what%20other%20people%20say.%20That%20is%20not%20why%20I%20play%20cricket.%20I%20do%20not%20play%20cricket%20to%20get%20the%20milestones.%20I%20want%20to%20win%20games.%20I%20love%20playing%20for%20a%20team%20and%20that%20is%20when%20I%20get%20the%20biggest%20buzz.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I'm%20probably%20a%20little%20bit%20flat%20now%2C%20because%20we%20have%20lost%204-1%20in%20this%20series.%20But%20I%20enjoyed%20this%20tour.%20I%20have%20been%20on%20tours%20to%20India%20before%20where%20little%20cracks%20start%20appearing%20in%20the%20team%20and%20that%20has%20not%20happened%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20would%20not%20be%20playing%20another%20Test%20match%20until%20West%20Indies%20arrives%20in%20the%20UK%20in%20July%20and%20by%20that%20time%2C%20Anderson%20would%20be%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20away%20from%20his%2042nd%20birthday.%20Having%20taken%2010%20wickets%20in%20four%20matches%20in%20India%20at%20an%20average%20of%2033.50%2C%20Anderson%20feels%20that%20he%20has%20enough%20in%20his%20tank%20fitness%20and%20form-wise%20to%20keep%20going%20and%20is%20in%20his%20%26quot%3Bbest%20shape%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20placed%20importance%20on%20working%20hard%20since%20his%20place%20is%20not%20fixed%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20excited%20for%20the%20summer.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20playing%20well%20and%20earn%20my%20place%20in%20the%20team.%20I%20am%20not%20getting%20any%20worse.%20I%20am%20definitely%20in%20the%20best%20shape%20I%20have%20ever%20been%20in.%20I%20like%20where%20my%20game%20is%20at%2C%20and%20I%20still%20have%20that%20enjoyment%20of%20turning%20up%20every%20day%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20better%20in%20the%20nets.%20My%20place%20in%20the%20team%20is%20not%20a%20given%20so%20I%20have%20got%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20prove%20am%20worth%20a%20place%20in%20the%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%