2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20replaced%20its%20earlier%20code%20regulating%20relations%20between%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20and%20doctors%20with%20a%20new%20one%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKnown%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Uniform%20Code%20of%20Pharmaceutical%20Marketing%20Practices%E2%80%99%20(UCPMP)%2C%20the%20notification%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stipulate%20that%20the%20code%20is%20mandatory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20works%20under%20the%20Union%20chemicals%20and%20fertilisers%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmaceuticals.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FUCPMP%25202024%2520for%2520website_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecode%E2%80%99s%20latest%20version%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20like%20its%20previous%20one%2C%20says%20that%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20must%20not%20bribe%20doctors%20in%20any%20form%20or%20even%20arrange%20for%20their%20travel%20facilities%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20healthcare%20professionals%20promoting%20or%20excessively%20prescribing%20a%20particular%20drug.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20why%20the%20code%20is%20crucial%20to%20curb%20unethical%20practices%20that%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20undertake%20in%20connivance%20with%20doctors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20the%20criticism%20that%20the%20previous%20version%20of%20the%20code%2C%20which%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmaceuticals.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FUCPMP.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enotified%20in%20December%202014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20attracted%20was%20related%20to%20its%20voluntary%20nature.%20There%20was%20no%20legal%20backing%20to%20its%20provisions%20and%20it%20therefore%20remained%20toothless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20long-pending%20demand%20of%20various%20health%20activists%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory.%20Even%20the%202017-18%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20insisted%20on%20making%20it%20mandatory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%20has%20now%20removed%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98voluntary%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20code%2C%20which%20was%20there%20in%20the%20previous%20version%2C%20it%20has%20stopped%20short%20of%20making%20it%20mandatory.%20It%20has%20now%20merely%20%E2%80%98requested%E2%80%99%20the%20pharmaceutical%20companies%E2%80%99%20associations%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20code%20is%20%E2%80%98implemented%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202024%20version%20of%20the%20UCPMP%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20associations%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3Erequested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20constitute%20an%20Ethics%20Committee%20for%20Pharmaceutical%20Marketing%20Practices%20(ECPMP)%2C%20set%20up%20a%20dedicated%20UCPMP%20portal%20on%20their%20website%2C%20and%20take%20further%20necessary%20steps%20towards%20implementation%20of%20this%20Code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmaceuticals.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual%2520Report%25202017-18.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2017-18%20annual%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20had%20noted%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUniform%20Code%20For%20Pharmaceuticals%20Marketing%20Practices%20(UCPMP)%20for%20Pharmaceutical%20as%20well%20as%20Medical%20Device%20Industry%20is%20being%20implemented%20w.e.f.%201.1.2015.%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20UCPMP%20has%20been%20reviewed%20in%20consultation%20of%20%5Bwith%5D%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20including%20NGOs%2FCivil%20Societies%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20it%20was%20felt%20that%20in%20order%20to%20implement%20it%20more%20effectively%2C%20it%20would%20be%20desirable%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20even%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20pharmaceuticals%20was%20working%20with%20the%20legal%20affairs%20department%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20making%20the%20code%20mandatory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20later%20changed%20its%20stand.%20In%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-supreme-court-pharma-doctor%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESupreme%20Court%20hearing%20in%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20government%20said%20it%20was%20not%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20code%20should%20be%20made%20mandatory.%20It%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20code%20in%20its%20previous%20form%20%E2%80%93%20voluntary%20%E2%80%93%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadequate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-supreme-court-pharma-doctor%5C%22%3EUnion%20Govt%20Flips%20Stance%2C%20Tells%20SC%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Push%20for%20Mandatory%20Rules%20to%20Curb%20Pharma-Doctor%20Nexus%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhither%20punishment%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20if%20the%20code%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20become%20mandatory%2C%20what%20punishment%20does%20it%20stipulate%20if%20a%20pharmaceutical%20company%20is%20indeed%20found%20bribing%20a%20doctor%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20punishment%2C%20in%20this%20version%20of%20the%20code%2C%20as%20in%20the%20previous%20one%2C%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20maximum%20that%20a%20pharma%20company%20concerned%20can%20face%20is%20that%20it%20would%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20association%20of%20the%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20of%20which%20it%20is%20a%20member.%20There%20is%20no%20penalty%20or%20scope%20of%20any%20other%20action%20against%20the%20company%20except%20it%20losing%20membership%20of%20the%20association%20that%20it%20is%20part%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20reporter%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Fthere-s-an-unhealthy-alliance-between-doctors-and-pharma-firms-64230%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efiled%20RTI%20applications%20in%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20ask%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20whether%20it%20was%20aware%20if%20even%20this%20mild%20punishment%20had%20been%20meted%20out%20to%20any%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20specifically%20named%2020%20pharma%20companies%20in%20the%20reply%20and%20said%20it%20was%20aware%20that%20they%20had%20violated%20the%20code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20action%20taken%20against%20them%2C%20it%20said%20their%20names%20had%20been%20forwarded%20to%20the%20pharmaceuticals%20associations%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20the%20India%20Pharmaceutical%20Association%20(IPA)%20to%20take%20%E2%80%98action%E2%80%99%20against%20all%20the%20firms%20charged%20with%20malpractice%20between%202015%20and%202016%2C%20and%20to%20the%20Indian%20Drug%20Manufacturers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(IDMA)%20as%20per%20UCPMP%20provisions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20previous%20version%20of%20the%20code%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20current%20one%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20whenever%20pharma%20associations%20take%20an%20action%2C%20they%20should%20put%20it%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20through%20their%20respective%20websites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20in%20a%20follow-up%20RTI%20query%2C%20it%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20punishment%20%E2%80%93%20the%20pharma%20company%20being%20removed%20from%20the%20association%20%E2%80%93%20the%20reply%20stayed%20silent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20what%20if%20the%20pharmaceutical%20company%20concerned%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20any%20of%20the%20associations%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20The%20code%20is%20silent%20in%20the%20recent%20version%2C%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20previous%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20nothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20one%20of%20the%2020%20pharma%20companies%20named%20as%20violators%20as%20part%20of%20RTI%20reply%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eactually%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20part%20of%20any%20association.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoctors%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20found%20being%20bribed%20by%20the%20pharma%20companies%2C%20can%20be%20punished%20as%20per%20another%20code%20of%20ethics%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20NMC%20revised%20its%20set%20of%20ethics%20and%20said%20doctors%2C%20besides%20facing%20suspension%20of%20their%20licence%20to%20practise%20if%20a%20violation%20was%20established%2C%20could%20also%20be%20asked%20to%20pay%20a%20monetary%20penalty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NMC%20code%20of%20ethics%20also%20barred%20doctors%20from%20attending%20conferences%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%20sponsored%20by%20pharma%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20and%20other%20groups%2C%20the%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnmc-puts-new-guidelines-on-doctors-ethics-in-abeyance-after-imas-meeting-with-health-minister%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eput%20its%20revised%20ethics%20under%20abeyance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20reverted%20to%20the%202002%20code%20for%20doctors%2C%20which%20said%20the%20state%20medical%20commissions%20could%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20suspend%20doctors%E2%80%99%20licenses%20for%20a%20period%20it%20thought%20was%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20it%20did%20not%20bar%20doctors%20from%20attending%20a%20pharma%20company-sponsored%20conference%2C%20which%20the%20now-abandoned%20code%20of%20last%20year%20had%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKey%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCPMP%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20key%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCPMP%20remain%20the%20same%20in%20the%20current%20version%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%20that%20the%20companies%20should%20not%20extend%20travel%20facilities%20inside%20or%20outside%20the%20country%20to%20healthcare%20professionals%20or%20their%20family%20members%20for%20attending%20medical%20conferences.%20It%20also%20bars%20companies%20from%20extending%20any%20hospitality%2C%20including%20hotel%20accommodation%2C%20to%20doctors%20attending%20medical%20conferences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20these%20provisions%20being%20there%20in%20the%202014%20code%20as%20well%2C%20there%20have%20been%20many%20instances%20of%20them%20being%20violated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Amitava%20Guha%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20Jan%20Swasthya%20Abhiyan%2C%20submitted%20proofs%20of%20a%20pharma%20company%20sponsoring%20trips%20to%20Vancouver%20for%2013%20doctors%2C%20paying%20the%20hotel%20bills%20of%20258%20doctors%20for%20attending%20a%20diabetes%20conference%20in%20Chennai%2C%20giving%20six%20doctors%20cash%20for%20a%20pleasure%20trip%20to%20Australia%20and%20paying%20up%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20each%20to%2058%20doctors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20reported%20many%20other%20violations%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20record%20of%20how%20many%20of%20these%20doctors%20got%20punished%20by%20the%20NMC%20%E2%80%93%20if%20indeed%20they%20were%20%E2%80%93%20and%20how%20many%20pharma%20companies%20faced%20removal%20from%20the%20associations%20they%20were%20part%20of%2C%20as%20a%20punishment%20prescribed%20under%20the%20UCPMP%E2%80%99s%202014%20version.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20version%20of%20the%20UCPMP%20also%20explicitly%20states%20that%20no%20gift%20should%20be%20offered%20for%20the%20personal%20benefit%20of%20any%20healthcare%20professional%20or%20their%20family%20members%20by%20any%20pharmaceutical%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20version%20also%20has%20a%20section%20on%20the%20organisation%20of%20medical%20conferences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20conferences%20have%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20because%20they%20are%20many%20a%20time%20organised%20by%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%20allegedly%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20part%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20organising%20these%20conferences%2C%20pharma%20companies%20incur%20huge%20expenditures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20code%20does%20allow%20them%20to%20continue%20organising%20these%20conferences%20but%20prohibits%20them%20from%20doing%20so%20in%20foreign%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20code%20also%20says%20that%20a%20pharmaceutical%20company%20organising%20such%20conferences%20should%20upload%20the%20details%20of%20its%20expenditure%20on%20its%20website%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20%E2%80%9Csubjected%20to%20independent%2C%20random%2C%20or%20risk-based%20audit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENon-adherence%20to%20any%20of%20these%20provisions%20could%20attract%20punishment%20for%20pharma%20firms%20as%20stated%20above.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710298826000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fnew-code-for-doctor-pharma-unethical-practices-notified-but-remains-non-mandatory%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20code%2C%20which%20bars%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20from%20bribing%20doctors%2C%20has%20undergone%20much-anticipated%20revision%20after%20ten%20years%20but%20fails%20to%20get%20teeth%20for%20its%20implementation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fnew-code-for-doctor-pharma-unethical-practices-notified-but-remains-non-mandatory%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UTA%20Accused%20of%20Fraud%2C%20Breach%20of%20Contract%20by%20MediaLink%20CEO%20Michael%20Kassan%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710297304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Futa-kassen.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235940093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20Talent%20Agency%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20breach%20of%20contract%20and%20fraud%20in%20relation%20to%20its%202021%20acquisition%20of%20the%20consultancy%20firm%20MediaLink.%20MediaLink%20founder%20and%20UTA%20partner%20Michael%20Kassen%2C%20whose%20exit%20from%20the%20company%20nearly%20a%20week%20ago%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20reported%2C%20claims%20that%20UTA%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Zimmer%20and%20two%20other%20top%20executives%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietymattdonnelly%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Futa-fraud-breach-of-contract-medialink-michael-kassan-1235940093%