22%3ESamvaad%2C%20enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20among%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20tribal%20gatherings%2C%20bringing%20together%20over%202%2C500%20people%20from%20200%20tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%2C%20which%20stepped%20into%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20has%20created%20a%20stable%20and%20consistent%20ecosystem%20for%20dialogue%20on%20tribal%20discourse.%20Tribes%20from%20across%20India%20come%20together%20to%20address%20issues%20affecting%20their%20communities%20and%20look%20for%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20brought%20together%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20over%20200%20tribes%20in%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010th%20edition%20commenced%20with%20the%20traditional%20beats%20of%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%2C%20dhols%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20musical%20instruments%2C%20commemorating%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20the%20iconic%20tribal%20freedom%20fighter%20from%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theme%20for%20this%20edition%20was%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%2C%20collectives%2C%20and%20changemakers%20associated%20with%20Samvaad%20since%20its%20inception.%20It%20acknowledged%20the%20impact%20of%20solution-driven%20dialogues%20and%20conversations%20from%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319311%2Fsheela-powel-helps-toda-women-sell-traditional-embroidery-shalom-ooty%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%20and%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction%20due%20to%20several%20reasons%20like%20lack%20of%20remuneration%2C%20migration%2C%20or%20the%20next%20generation%20does%20not%20want%20to%20do%20it.%20We%20have%20been%20working%20on%20reviving%20the%20art%20by%20solving%20these%20problems.%20Art%20is%20directly%20related%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smita%20Verma%2C%20Lead%20%E2%80%93%20Gender%20%26amp%3B%20Community%20Enterprise%2C%20TSF%2C%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20are%20proud%20of%20our%20identity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Brijesh%2C%20the%20Sankalp%20Foundation%20involves%20around%20300%20people%20from%2072%20villages.%20This%20collective%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20artists%20to%20learn%20about%20current%20trends%20and%20marketing%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20beautiful%20chaos%20when%20multiple%20tribal%20communities%20come%20together%20to%20make%20the%20products.%20Although%20the%20communities%20have%20different%20traditions%2C%20their%20turmoil%20is%20mostly%20similar%2C%20which%20then%20becomes%20a%20point%20of%20unity.%20People%20that%20were%20once%20ashamed%20of%20their%20skills%20and%20identities%20are%20now%20proudly%20wearing%20and%20adorning%20them%20while%20making%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Brijesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20close%20to%20nature%2C%20the%20Sankalp%20Foundation%20is%20happy%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20sustainability%20route.%20All%20their%20wooden%20products%20are%20made%20from%20fallen%3Cem%3E%20chikoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20twigs%20and%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustainability%20is%20also%20a%20winner%20in%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20neighbouring%20handloom%20stall%20belonging%20to%20the%20Bodo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331624%2Fassam-man-quits-his-job-to-make-sustainable-toys-that-represent-assams-tribes-and-culture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribes%20of%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20cotton%20clothes%20are%20made%20from%20natural%20colours%20that%20last%20forever%20and%20are%20also%20good%20for%20the%20skin.%20We%20make%20colours%20from%20turmeric%2C%20leaves%20from%20plants%20and%20a%20few%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaison%20Bhramo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotisankar%20Sahu%20of%20the%20Sabar%20tribe%20from%20Odisha%20is%20here%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20best%20benefit%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20is%20making%20his%20digital%20debut.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20group%20of%2070%20people%20who%20make%20brass%20showpieces.%20We%20always%20get%20orders%20after%20we%20return%20home%20from%20the%20conclave.%20Samvaad%20is%20a%20good%20platform%20to%20preserve%20our%20culture%20and%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20the%20exceptional%20skills%20that%20we%20learnt%20from%20our%20ancestors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20exposure%2C%20the%20artisans%20are%20also%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%20their%20traditions.%20Sangeeta%20Meda%20from%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20second%20time%20here%2C%20and%20people%20always%20ask%20us%20about%20our%20history%20and%20the%20significance%20of%20our%20Bhil%20Pithora%20paintings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ancestors%20would%20make%20these%20dotted%20paintings%20on%20walls%20during%20festivities.%20Gradually%2C%20they%20moved%20onto%20paper.%20Our%20paintings%20tell%20the%20stories%20of%20our%20origin%20and%20who%20we%20are.%20While%20selling%2C%20we%20let%20the%20customers%20know%20our%20intention%20behind%20choosing%20a%20particular%20colour%20and%20theme.%20They%20feel%20connected%20to%20us.%20My%20grandmother%2C%20Buri%20Bai%2C%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20preservation%20efforts.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20carry%20forward%20her%20legacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20shares%20that%20the%20family%20starts%20the%20work%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20Samvaad%20as%20it%20takes%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20She%20happily%20adds%20that%20their%20paintings%20sell%20like%20hotcakes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%20is%20Dinabandhu%20Soren%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ho%20tribe.%20It%20is%20his%20ninth%20year%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20each%20year%20has%20been%20fruitful%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelling%20our%20paintings%20was%20a%20loss-making%20business%20in%20Ganjam%20district%20till%20we%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20The%20workshops%20helped%20create%20a%20balance%20between%20our%20traditional%20painting%20techniques%20and%20the%20market%20demands.%20With%20a%20few%20tweaks%20and%20the%20right%20market%20linkages%2C%20we%20sold%20%3Cem%3Egond%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejuang%3C%2Fem%3E%20paintings%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20across%20India.%20We%20were%20even%20selected%20to%20do%20live%20sketching%20at%20G20%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20an%20art%20teacher%20at%20Srujanika%2C%20a%20women-led%20self-help%20group.%20Srujanika%20has%2030%20women%20who%20make%20paintings%2C%20Army%20uniforms%2C%20and%20other%20merchandise%20like%20%3Cem%3Edupattas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20T-shirts%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20profits%2C%20the%20women%20are%20passing%20on%20the%20skills%20to%20their%20children%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYazile%20from%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Rengma%20tribe%20has%20a%20similar%20journey%2C%20from%20no%20sales%20to%20selling%20pan%20India.%20%E2%80%9CNearly%20every%20homemaker%20in%20the%20Dimapur%20area%20can%20make%20our%20traditional%20attire%2C%20%3Cem%3Emekhelas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20shawls.%20The%20skills%20were%20there%2C%20but%20the%20selling%20opportunity%20was%20missing.%20We%20attended%20a%20workshop%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20learned%20that%20new%20designs%20can%20be%20implemented%20on%20pillow%20covers%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20etc.%20In%20our%20second%20year%2C%20we%20did%20that%20and%20made%20profits.%20I%20also%20made%20friends%20from%20other%20tribal%20communities%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20fashion%20trends%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yazile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20and%20craft%20workshops%20helped%20artists%20like%20Yazile%20and%20Dinabandhu%20post-pandemic%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20and%20selling%20at%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20building%20online%20market%20links%20for%2026%20tribal%20communities%20representing%2030%20art%20forms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3EToda%3C%2Fem%3E%20embroidery%20of%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Cem%3EMuga%20%3C%2Fem%3Esilk%20of%20Assam%2C%20and%20more%20as%20popular%20as%20%3Cem%3EBanarasi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIkat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChikankari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20in%20experts%20from%20NIFT%20and%20NID%20to%20impart%20the%20skills%2C%20colour%20combinations%2C%20motifs%2C%20etc%2C%20that%20meet%20customer%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrends%20in%20the%20metro%20change%20fast%2C%20so%20we%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20change%20their%20cultural%20identity.%C2%A0%20But%20they%20can%20experiment%20with%20colours%20and%20motifs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20pastel%20colour%20is%20in%20the%20market%2C%20infuse%20those%20colours%20in%20the%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thronging%20crowds%20at%20handicraft%20stalls%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20workshops%20were%20beneficial.%20Chaaya%20Saraiwala%2C%20an%20attendee%2C%20purchased%20Yazile%E2%80%99s%20shawls%20and%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20fridge%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20attending%20Samvaad%20and%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20myriad%20products%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20have%20bought%20a%20few%20items%20for%20my%20family.%20Each%20product%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20history%20that%20we%20do%20not%20know%2C%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20conclaves%20like%20Samvaad%20are%20changing%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Tata%20Samvaad%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20artisans%20from%20indigenous%20tribes%20across%20India%20shone%20a%20spotlight%20on%20fading%20tribal%20arts%2C%20reviving%20them%20with%20contemporary%20flair%20to%20build%20livelihoods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astronauts%20leave%20treats%20behind%20on%20space%20station%20as%20they%20splash%20down%20after%20months%20in%20orbit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-nasa-astronauts_6488028.jpg%3F20240312133613%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20astronauts%20from%20four%20different%20countries%20have%20safely%20returned%20to%20Earth%20as%20they%20splashed%20down%20near%20Florida%20after%20199%20days%20in%20orbit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A200%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22