mun%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%20helps%20control%20sugar%3B%20you%20will%20not%20find%20this%20anywhere%20else%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20potential%20customer%20at%20his%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conviction%20in%20his%20tone%20changed%20as%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20team%20asked%20about%20how%20his%20community%20cuisine%20could%20help%20his%20tribe%20do%20better.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CProvide%20us%20platforms%20like%20Samvaad%20where%20we%20can%20share%20our%20culture%20and%20food%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20help%20us%20tell%20our%20own%20stories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20preserving%20his%20tribal%20identity%20through%20cuisine%20mirrored%20the%20essence%20of%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF)%2C%20which%20brings%20together%20the%20diverse%20tribes%20of%20India%20on%20one%20platform%20for%20a%20five-day-long%20festivity%2C%20which%20lets%20everyone%20immerse%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274494%2Fgond-artist-artwork-museums-france-usa-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20belongs%20to%20one%20of%20the%20200%20tribal%20communities%20participating%20in%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20tribal%20conclave%20which%20brings%20together%20tribes%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20beyond.%20It%20is%20emerging%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20platforms%20for%20dialogues%20on%20tribal%20discourse%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Performanc