ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324508%2Fbest-pet-friendly-homestays-across-india-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20travel%20buddies%20%3C%2Fa%3Esince%20they%20were%20in%20college.%20While%20the%20life%20of%20the%20couple%20changed%20when%20they%20had%20kids%2C%20the%20travel%20lover%20in%20them%20never%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20cut%20their%20expenses%20on%20travel%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20mini%20home%20on%20wheels.%20They%20bought%20a%20Force%20Traveller%203350%20and%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20caravan%20of%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20they%20find%20time%20between%20their%20jobs%3F%20Deepak%20has%20a%20transferable%20job%2C%20which%20means%20moving%20around%20the%20country%20every%20two%20years.%20He%20makes%20sure%20to%20use%20his%20leaves%20judiciously%20and%20embarks%20on%20a%20trip%20every%20quarter.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20taken%20four%20trips%20in%20their%20van%20%E2%80%94%20Leh%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709958600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-20-1709904937.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20choosing%20the%20right%20vehicle%20to%20planning%20your%20travel%20without%20quitting%20your%20jobs%2C%20this%20list%20of%20tips%20and%20tricks%20from%20seasoned%20caravan%20travellers%20will%20help%20you%20make%20a%20perfect%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344433%2Fvan-life-in-india-tips-caravan-travel-wfh-work-from-home-travelling-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20by%20IIT%20Grads%20Helps%20Indian%20Homes%20Run%20on%20Zero%20Electricity%2C%20Earns%20Rs%20200%20Crore%20in%20Revenues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202020%2C%20entrepreneurs%20Neeraj%20Jain%20and%20Nikhil%20Nahar%20made%20a%20decision%20that%20would%20confound%20most%20entrepreneurs.%20Despite%20running%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20bootstrapped%20and%20profitable%20startup%20centred%20on%20setting%20up%20solar%20power%20installations%20for%20large%20corporations%20since%202015%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20make%2C%20what%20many%20felt%20at%20the%20time%20was%2C%20a%20risky%20pivot%20towards%20the%20(B2C)%20residential%20solar%20segment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20them%20make%20that%20pivot%2C%20Neeraj%20roped%20in%20fellow%20entrepreneur%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT-Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E%20graduate%20Shreya%20Mishra%2C%20who%20had%20prior%20experience%20of%20running%20a%20consumer%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20were%20only%2026%20and%2027%20respectively%20when%20they%20founded%20SolarSquare%20in%202015.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20I%20founded%20Flyrobe%2C%20a%20fashion%20rental%20startup.%20It%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20world%20of%20solar%20energy.%20I%20sold%20my%20startup%20in%202019%2C%20and%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20my%20husband%20Neeraj%20convinced%20me%20to%20join%20SolarSquare.%20He%20was%20an%20engineer%20with%20banking%20experience%20but%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20with%20deep%20meaning%20and%20purpose.%20While%20he%20had%20a%20good%20grasp%20of%20the%20solar%20market%2C%20he%20wanted%20my%20expertise%20in%20building%20consumer%20businesses.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20started%20experimenting%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20more%20B2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shreya%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SolarSquare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20pivot%20because%20the%20industrial%20segment%20is%20very%20different.%20As%20a%20company%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20segment%2C%20SolarSquare%20was%20setting%20up%20massive%20and%20customised%20solar%20power%20installations%20worth%20a%20few%20crores%20for%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20This%20is%20unlike%20the%20residential%20sector%20where%20they%20are%20dealing%20with%20individual%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20took%20a%20very%20bold%20call%20to%20experiment%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20because%20they%20understood%20the%20massive%20business%20opportunity%20it%20offered%20at%20a%20time%20when%20no%20organised%20company%20in%20the%20solar%20energy%20space%20saw%20it.%20They%20saw%20that%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20looked%20like%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future.%20If%20they%20were%20to%20commit%20to%20this%2C%20they%20had%20to%20focus%20all%20their%20energies%20on%20it.%20That%20was%20a%20major%20inflexion%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residential%20solar%20segment%20presented%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future%20because%20average%20Indian%20households%20were%20struggling%20with%20rising%20electricity%20bills%20thanks%20to%20increasing%20tariffs%20and%20regular%20incidences%20of%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%20Rising%20electricity%20costs%20in%20many%20states%20made%20it%20imperative%20for%20consumers%20to%20explore%20alternative%20solutions.%20One%20viable%20solution%20for%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20residential%20societies%20was%20to%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%20power%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Shreya%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20residential%20segment%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%20a%20lot%20of%20standardisation%20in%20solar%20installations%20that%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20scale.%20Imagine%20doing%20tiny%20solar%20installations%20that%20are%20customised%20to%20each%20home!%20It%E2%80%99s%20too%20complex%20a%20process%20for%20a%20B2C%20operation.%20We%20standardised%20everything%20and%20made%20prefabricated%20ready-to-install%20solar%20kits%2C%20which%20get%20installed%20in%20just%20six%20hours.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20underwent%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20innovation%20for%20this%20segment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20three%20and%20half%20years%20later%2C%20SolarSquare%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20residential%20solar%20brand%20in%20India%20with%20a%20consumer%20base%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20over%20100%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311732%2Fmumbai-sustainable-housing-society-saves-water-electricity-navin-chandra-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20societies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20Shreya%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20serendipity%20led%20us%20here.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20operational%20in%2016%20cities%20spread%20across%20eight%20states.%20Over%20two%20rounds%20of%20funding%2C%20we%20have%20raised%20about%20Rs%20130%20crore%20and%20we%E2%80%99ll%20be%20doing%20close%20to%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20revenues%20in%20this%20financial%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20about%2020%25%20of%20SolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20business%20still%20lies%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20solar%20segment%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20pivoted%20close%20to%2080%25%20of%20their%20business%20towards%20the%20residential%20segment.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20have%20also%20doubled%20in%20size%20as%20a%20business%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%2080%25%20of%20our%20business%20is%20in%20the%20residential%20segment%20where%20we%20work%20with%20individual%20homes%20(2BHK%2C%203BHK)%20and%20residential%20societies.%20RWAs%20buy%20solar%20power%20installations%20for%20their%20common%20areas%20like%20lifts%2C%20water%20pumps%2C%20street%20lights%2C%20etc.%20Many%20of%20the%20high-rise%20apartments%20you%20see%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20are%20SolarSquare%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zero%20electricity%20with%20solar%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344445%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SolarSquare%20Team%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20doubt%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20Government%20had%20set%20a%20target%20of%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20in%20one%20crore%20households%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20When%20SolarSquare%20decided%20to%20pivot%20to%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20in%20late%202020%2C%20this%20major%20market%20opportunity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20families%20weren%E2%80%99t%20aware%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20solar.%20People%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20basics.%20Many%20people%20confuse%20rooftop%20solar%20installations%20with%20water%20heaters.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20you%20could%20power%20your%20home%20with%20solar.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20awareness%20levels%20were%20very%20nascent%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20first%20mandate%20was%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20on%20the%20back%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceducational%20marketing%20and%20trust.%E2%80%9D%20To%20that%20end%2C%20they%20published%20videos%2C%20content%2C%20and%20blogs%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20influencers%20to%20create%20awareness.%20They%20have%20also%20published%20a%20free%20homeowner%E2%80%99s%20guide%20to%20going%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20installing%20anything%2C%20we%20will%20help%20a%20homeowner%20understand%20why%20solar%20is%20good%20for%20them%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20solar%20installation%20is%20good%20for%20their%20home.%20We%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20first%20educate%20people%20before%20selling%20them%20anything.%20See%2C%20there%20was%20rampant%20mis-selling%20in%20this%20industry.%20Residential%20solar%20is%20a%20fragmented%20and%20unorganised%20market%20involving%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20operators%20who%20do%20this%20as%20a%20side%20business.%20People%20were%20sold%20second%20hand%20or%20rejected%20panels%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20authenticate%20warranty%20or%20quality%20of%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20many%20were%20sold%20solar%20power%20installations%20without%20after-sales%20service.%20If%20you%20are%20buying%20solar%2C%20buying%20the%20right%20after-sales%20service%20is%20very%20important%20because%2C%20without%20it%2C%20your%20investment%20goes%20down%20the%20drain.%20We%20had%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20these%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20SolarSquare%20was%20convincing%20potential%20investors%20that%20their%20decision%20to%20foray%20into%20the%20residential%20segment%20made%20business%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20went%20out%20to%20raise%20funds%2C%20potential%20investors%20thought%20that%20residential%20solar%20is%20a%20small%20market.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20more%20engaged%20in%20fintech%20and%20e-commerce.%20They%20felt%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20very%20brick-and-mortar%20business%20where%20you%20have%20to%20go%20from%20one%20home%20to%20another%2C%20educate%20people%2C%20close%20an%20order%2C%20install%20panels%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20maintain%20them%20for%20years.%20Nobody%20understood%20this%20market%20and%20its%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20June%202022%2C%20Shreya%20claimed%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98%2450%20billion%20opportunity%E2%80%99%20based%20on%20her%20estimates.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20bold%20claim%20back%20then%20given%20how%20international%20market%20research%20and%20advisory%20companies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECustom%20Market%20Insights%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20the%20entire%20Indian%20solar%20energy%20market%20was%20worth%20%2438%20billion%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20back%2C%20I%20probably%20wildly%20underestimated%20the%20market.%20With%20one%20crore%20homes%20potentially%20going%20solar%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20this%20market%20will%20probably%20see%20%2425%20billion.%20In%20a%20decade%2C%20this%20could%20very%20well%20be%20a%20%2475%20billion%20to%20%24100%20billion%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20unique%20time%20in%20history%20where%20you%20can%20create%20a%20consumer%20brand%20in%20energy.%20Otherwise%2C%20energy%20has%20always%20been%20the%20game%20of%20large%20corporations%20and%20Government-owned%20power%20plants.%20Energy%20is%20now%20personal%20and%20private%2C%20and%20we%20can%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289075%2Fisb-grad-helps-large-fmcg-brands-recycle-plastic-packaging-reduce-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20it.%20Investors%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20build%20their%20understanding%20of%20the%20possibilities%20in%20this%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22You%20will%20get%20zero%20electricity%20bill%20by%20going%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3A%20Helping%20homeowners%20go%20solar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20go%20solar%20with%20SolarSquare%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20can%20a%20homeowner%20in%20India%20install%20solar%20power%20in%20their%20homes%20with%20SolarSquare%3F%20A%20journey%20with%20them%20begins%20with%20registering%20an%20inquiry%20either%20on%20their%20website%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303367%2Fbengaluru-women-teach-how-to-compost-grow-vegetables-at-home-using-whatsapp-group-urban-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20customers%20register%20a%20query%2C%20SolarSquare%20sets%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98free%20solar%20consultation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20solar%20consultant%2C%20a%20trained%20expert%2C%20will%20visit%20your%20home%2C%20survey%20your%20roof%2C%20understand%20your%20electricity%20requirements%2C%20study%20your%20electricity%20bills%2C%20and%20guide%20you%20to%20the%20right%20solar%20solution%20for%20your%20home.%20They%20will%20also%20explain%20how%20solar%20power%20works%2C%20what%20are%20the%20different%20technology%20choices%20available%2C%20etc.%20We%20consult%20the%20customer%20with%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20their%20home%2C%20answer%20all%20their%20queries%2C%20and%20only%20then%20comes%20the%20question%20of%20selling%20anything%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zero%20electricity%20bills%20are%20possible%20with%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFamilies%20are%20first%20explained%20the%20process%2C%20cost%20and%20benefits%20of%20going%20solar.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20many%20consumers%20understand%20the%20benefits%20of%20going%20solar.%20Whatever%20money%20they%20put%20into%20installing%20solar%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20recover%20their%20investment%20in%20three%20to%20five%20years%20depending%20on%20the%20electricity%20tariff%20and%20then%20enjoy%2020%20to%2022%20years%20of%20free%20electricity.%20However%2C%20the%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20install%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20is%20often%20difficult%20for%20most%20middle-class%20families%20in%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this%20consultation%2C%20we%20also%20take%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20card%2C%20check%20his%20loan%20EMI%20eligibility%2C%20and%20present%20the%20EMI%20schemes%20we%20can%20offer%20to%20them.%20People%20can%20go%20solar%20on%20a%20six-month%20zero-cost%20EMI%2C%2012-month%20EMI%2C%20or%2060-month%20EMI.%20That%20makes%20it%20an%20affordable%20proposition.%20Also%2C%20in%20case%20of%2060-month%20EMI%2C%20their%20initial%20down%20payment%20to%20us%20gets%20covered%20through%20the%20subsidy%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20power%20a%202%20to%203-BHK%20home%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247226%2Fbengaluru-startup-clairco-innovation-air-pollution-turn-ac-into-air-filter-aayush-jha-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20consumer%20will%20need%20a%203-kW%20to%204-kW%20solar%20installation.%20If%20such%20homes%20have%20an%20air%20conditioner%2C%20they%20may%20require%205-kW%20to%206-kW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20commonly%20sold%20residential%20rooftop%20solar%20installation%20is%203-kW.%20A%20solar%20kit%20for%20this%20energy%20requirement%20is%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Government%20covers%20Rs%2078%2C000%20as%20a%20subsidy%20(under%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98PM-Surya%20Ghar%3A%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%E2%80%99).%20The%20consumer%20ends%20up%20paying%20only%20about%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjClnfkmeWKY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22New%20Subsidy%20Alert%20Feb%202024%20l%20Prime%20Minister%20Surya%20Ghar%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20this%203-kW%20system%2C%20consumers%20end%20up%20saving%20Rs%203%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20in%20electricity%20bills.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20this%20amounts%20to%20approximately%20Rs%2036%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20electricity%20savings.%20In%20about%20three%20to%20four%20years%2C%20you%20can%20recover%20all%20your%20initial%20investment.%20Following%20this%2C%20this%20solar%20installation%20can%20give%20you%20free%20electricity%20for%20the%20next%2020%20to%2025%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20consumer%20on%20a%20five-year%20EMI%2C%20their%20net%20investment%20comes%20down%20to%20zero%20because%20their%20down%20payment%20gets%20covered%20by%20the%20subsidy%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%20and%20monthly%20EMIs%20are%20covered%20through%20monthly%20electricity%20savings%20achieved%20after%20going%20solar.%20In%20net%20terms%2C%20the%20family%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20arrange%20any%20substantial%20sums.%20We%20call%20this%20the%20zero%20investment%20scheme%20of%20solar%2C%20which%20we%20educate%20the%20consumer%20about%20during%20a%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fwhgxo61Rm30%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fwhgxo61Rm30%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20family%20(consumer)%20decides%20to%20book%20their%20services%2C%20the%20startup%20draws%20up%20a%20detailed%20technical%20design%2C%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20their%20Government%20permits%2C%20and%20applies%20for%20their%20subsidy.%20After%20the%20consumer%20has%20approved%20the%20final%20design%2C%20they%20pay%20an%20advance%20which%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20subsidy%2C%20and%20then%2C%20the%20company%20delivers%20their%20ready-to-install%20solar%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ready-to-install%20kit%20includes%20our%20trademark%20Wind%20Pro%20Mount%20elevated%20structures%2C%20which%20are%20also%20known%20as%20module-mounted%20structures.%20Measuring%20about%20six%20feet%20tall%2C%20these%20structures%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20our%20installations%20holding%20up%20the%20panels.%20These%20structures%20are%20very%20sturdy%2C%20come%20with%20a%2010-year%20warranty%2C%20zero-rust%20guarantee%2C%20and%20certification%20from%20IIT-Bombay%20that%20even%20during%20a%20cyclone%20with%20wind%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20170%20kmph%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20rooftop%20solar%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20these%20solar%20installations%20are%20subject%20to%20external%20weather%2C%20elevated%2C%20and%20on%20top%20of%20a%20roof%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20high%20wind%20speed%20pressure.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20durable.%20We%20install%20our%20solar%20kit%20in%20just%20six%20to%20seven%20hours.%20Once%20installed%2C%20the%20customer%20requires%20an%20inspection%20from%20their%20local%20power%20discom.%20Once%20the%20site%20is%20inspected%2C%20their%20final%20bank%20details%20are%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Government%20portal%20and%20the%20subsidy%20comes%20into%20their%20bank%20account%20within%20just%2030%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Government%20recently%20launched%20the%20National%20Portal%20for%20Rooftop%20Solar%20on%20the%20back%20of%20which%20all%20of%20these%20Government%20subsidies%20and%20applications%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20care%20of%20all%20these%20applications%20for%20the%20consumer.%20We%20take%20care%20of%20Government%20permits%2C%20subsidy%20applications%2C%20EMI%20applications%2C%20inspections%2C%20design%2C%20procurement%2C%20etc.%20We%20are%20a%20full-stacked%20brand%20that%20offers%20end-to-end%20solutions%20for%20the%20Indian%20consumer%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20installation%20comes%20the%20most%20important%20part%20%E2%80%94%20after-sale%20service.%20India%20is%20a%20country%20where%20roofs%20are%20subject%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20dust%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20external%20weather%20conditions.%20These%20elements%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20rooftop%20solar%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20in%20which%20we%20take%20care%20of%20everything%20from%20panel%20deep%20cleaning%20to%20technical%2C%20mechanical%2C%20and%20electrical%20maintenance.%20Once%20installed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20roof%20and%20solar%20energy%20but%20our%20responsibility.%20As%20a%20policy%2C%20we%20sell%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20so%20that%20consumers%20can%20enjoy%20the%20benefits%20of%20zero-electricity%20bills%20year%20after%20year.%20Consumers%20can%20renew%20their%20after-sale%20care%20plan%20with%20us%20after%20these%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20rooftop%20solar%20systems%20as%20an%20investment%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20seeing%2020-25%25%20IRR%20(internal%20rate%20of%20return)%20if%20it%20gives%20you%20the%20right%20performance.%20Maintenance%20is%20important%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20realise%20that%2020-25%25%20IRR.%20Every%20month%20or%20three%20months%2C%20a%20trained%20SolarSquare%20technician%20will%20come%20to%20your%20home%2C%20do%20a%20complete%20technical%20check%2C%20electrical%20maintenance%2C%20and%20mechanical%20check%2C%20and%20do%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20to%20ensure%20any%20hard%20dust%20or%20bird%20droppings%20are%20removed.%20Following%20this%20check%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20spike%20in%20power%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Achieve%20zero%20electricity%20bills%20with%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20residential%20solar%20installation%20set%20up%20by%20SolarSquare%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20moving%20forward%20for%20companies%20like%20SolarSquare%20will%20be%20managing%20solar%20panels%20that%20reach%20the%20end%20of%20their%20lives.%20These%20discarded%20panels%20are%20often%20left%20strewn%20around%20or%20eventually%20get%20mixed%20up%20with%20domestic%20solid%20waste%20and%20end%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20International%20Renewable%20Energy%20Agency%2C%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amounts%20of%20annual%20(solar%20panel)%20waste%20are%20anticipated%20by%20the%20early%202030s%E2%80%9D%20and%20could%20touch%2078%20million%20tonnes%20by%202050.%20Shreya%2C%20however%2C%20believes%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20extend%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20used%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20maintain%20your%20rooftop%20solar%20installation%20well%2C%20it%20can%20last%20up%20to%2030-35%20years.%20So%2C%20once%20a%20consumer%20retires%20their%20solar%20rooftop%20system%2C%20they%20can%20donate%20the%20panels%20to%20non-profits%20working%20for%20a%20worthy%20cause.%20These%20panels%20can%20run%20for%20another%2010%20years%20because%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20maintained%20so%20well.%20These%20solar%20panels%20can%20have%20a%20second-hand%20life%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20does%20admit%20that%20ventures%20like%20SolarSquare%20will%20have%20to%20devise%20comprehensive%20plans%20to%20recycle%20decommissioned%20panels.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20only%20a%20nine-year-old%20company%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20solar%20installations%20that%20have%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20life.%20The%20question%20of%20disposal%20and%20recycling%20is%20important.%20Thankfully%2C%20you%20already%20have%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20that%20can%20recycle%2070%25%20of%20the%20components%20and%20materials%20used%20to%20make%20solar%20panels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Sustainable%20Technologies%20(CST)%2C%20led%20by%20Dr%20Monto%20Mani%20and%20operating%20out%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287506%2Fiisc-bengaluru-reuse-upcycle-old-decommissioned-solar-panels-as-building-material%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Bengaluru%2C%20is%20exploring%20whether%20old%20discarded%20solar%20panels%20can%20be%20upcycled%20as%20a%20building%20material.%20With%20this%2C%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20extend%20the%20panels%E2%80%99%20useful%20life%20by%20a%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20future%20as%20a%20business%2C%20things%20look%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%2030%20crore%20in%20their%20Seed%20round.%20During%20their%20Series%20A%20round%20in%20October%202022%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CLower%20Carbon%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20climate%20tech%20funds%2C%20is%20our%20shareholder.%20It%20was%20their%20first%20investment%20in%20India.%20We%20also%20have%20Elevation%20Capital%2C%20who%20are%20investors%20in%20Swiggy%20and%20Urban%20Company%2C%20and%20other%20notable%20investors%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20according%20to%20a%20November%202023%20report%20by%20the%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW)%2C%20more%20than%2025%20crore%20households%20in%20India%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20deploy%20637%20GW%20of%20solar%20energy%20capacity%20on%20rooftops.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20same%2C%20%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20the%20CEEW%20report%20found%20that%20deploying%20just%20one-third%20of%20this%20total%20solar%20technical%20potential%20could%20support%20the%20entire%20electricity%20demand%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20residential%20sector%20(~310%20TWh).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20ventures%20like%20SolarSquare%2C%20the%20opportunities%20are%20massive%20and%20the%20future%20looks%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SolarSquare)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHomeowner%E2%80%99s%20Guide%20to%20Buying%20Rooftop%20Solar%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2Ffill-download-form%3Futm_source%3DPR%26utm_medium%3DOrganic%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia08032024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98SolarSquare%E2%80%99s%2